text.tspan: Share of US land area with unusually high annual precipitation
Share of land area in the United States which experienced unusually high annual precipitation in a given year. This
compares actual yearly precipitation totals with expected totals based on historical data.
Source: NOAA (National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration) via the US EPA
